channel.title: DeltaScape again
channel.description:
Hello, sorry for double post... Well, got the DeltaScape running. But now, all types of status checkers says it's online, but none of my friends can connect, only me? I'm using DeltaScaoe source and DeltaScape client V4. Is there something I have to change in client?
Thanks ~ Extoz
PS. Not going to run Delta, just wanna show some friends. :D
